{"tid":1550643,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"你班撚樣肯打柒班左膠未？","createTime":"2019-09-07T16:56:58.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-14T10:19:56.000Z","uid":73143,"like":42,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":38,"replies":[{"pid":"95ee96cb8ecfb198bfdb5c1b14a8ced3eec53f9c","tid":1550643,"uid":73143,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:56:58.000Z","msg":"我就見一次打一次"},{"pid":"7fce8aee7bba08e3e3ded8cbb169a635798dfe6a","tid":1550643,"uid":123991,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:37.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><div style=\"text-align: center;\">出黎呀，自由閪！</div></strong></span><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>不闖入、不塗鴉、不鐳射</strong></span></span><br />\n如有發現，批淮大家往死裡打 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<strong><span style=\"color: red;\">明日之公眾集會(遮打花園)及公眾遊行(前往美領)已獲發不反對通知書。</span></strong><br />\n<br />\n集會部分<br />\n地點：中環遮打花園<br />\n時間：13:30 - 18:30<br />\n四節主題：時代子民、獄中讚歌、審判將至、天佑美國<br />\n<br />\n※※ 遮打現場將收集香港人權與民主宣言聯署至14:30﹐隨後出發向美領遞交 ※※<br />\n<br />\n遊行部分<br />\n集合地點：中環遮打花園金鐘道出口<br />\n集合時間：14:30<br />\n遊行路線：遮打花園經花園道往下亞厘畢道巴士站公眾活動區，向美國領事館遞交請願信<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ZY3Vs7C.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FZY3Vs7C.jpg&h=2d1d3d5a&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"11857bfcd09fe29f81fd9fe6fcb2ec485084a32a","tid":1550643,"uid":85708,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"打左膠有撚用咩 on9"},{"pid":"c5739427c42771fd8cdf697ad4e49a43a1b243ca","tid":1550643,"uid":73143,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"quote":{"pid":"11857bfcd09fe29f81fd9fe6fcb2ec485084a32a","tid":1550643,"uid":85708,"like":2,"dislike":17,"score":-15,"citedBy":6,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T16:58:51.000Z","msg":"打左膠有撚用咩 on9"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:19.000Z","msg":"你條左膠咪比我見到你，一定打撚柒你<br />\n害死咁多手足"},{"pid":"9df1673d82631da488ae439cfc88a72c7231bb59","tid":1550643,"uid":257422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:01:58.000Z","msg":"<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">我警告你班仆街！</span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: gold;\">聽日啲<span style=\"color: red;\">美國</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">國旗</span>唔好周圍掉！<br />\n路邊見到唔該即刻幫手執返！<br />\n完咗活動攞返屋企收藏！</span></span><br />\n</div><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/evxvjtB.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FevxvjtB.jpg&h=73325a8f&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\"> 快啲聽熟加背歌詞，<br />\n唱得莊嚴啲！</span>\t<a href=\"https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fyoutu.be%2FPWMy7Rpk5Bo&d=2M92vpXgCVs0KpVIJKRQC%2Br6kk4zB%2BnGw4DSdwpbM%2Bg%3D&h=61838f6b\" target=\"_blank\">https://youtu.be/PWMy7Rpk5Bo</a><br />\n</span><br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\"><br />\n分段背易啲背：<br />\n<br />\n<div style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">Oh, say can you see,</span></span><br />\nBy the dawn's early light,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">What so proudly we hailed,</span><br />\nAt the twilight's last gleaming?<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Whose broad stripes and bright stars,</span><br />\nThrough the perilous fight,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">O'er the ramparts we watched,</span><br />\nWere so gallantly streaming.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">And the rocket's red glare,</span><br />\nThe bombs bursting in air,<br />\n<span style=\"color: gold;\">Gave proof through the night,</span><br />\nThat our flag was still there.<br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">Oh say does that star spangled banner yet wave,</span><br />\n<br />\nFor the land of the free, and the home of the brave.</div><br />\n<br />\n聽日見！</span>"},{"pid":"e020ad4b535a3a84d034a46e88c14d6e6b99223e","tid":1550643,"uid":85708,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你打撚完咁點? 你話我知"},{"pid":"2549373ef0247ca7e99a86c489df3a6ec865c489","tid":1550643,"uid":224678,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/ykagZXe.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FykagZXe.gif&h=a4c0e484&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"0d16cf2ae21694d31f615d388d45bb7f07a1d528","tid":1550643,"uid":294,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:03:35.000Z","msg":"辣低佢就夠, 唔洗打"},{"pid":"8e5323bd2c814bdad58e08f0fdafd073b4a2f14d","tid":1550643,"uid":73143,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"e020ad4b535a3a84d034a46e88c14d6e6b99223e","tid":1550643,"uid":85708,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你打撚完咁點? 你話我知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:09.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\"><strong>打撚到你班左膠唔撚敢再阻住手足做野！！！！</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">左膠死全家</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"226064c622835b048b80c9b174460e4fa025759f","tid":1550643,"uid":63154,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e020ad4b535a3a84d034a46e88c14d6e6b99223e","tid":1550643,"uid":85708,"like":0,"dislike":6,"score":-6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:02:16.000Z","msg":"你打撚完咁點? 你話我知"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:04:17.000Z","msg":"咪少個害人精囉，點？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e71d39d62368b059d36d1e2b8fb11b24e3449c32","tid":1550643,"uid":252492,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:05:32.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">左膠永遠都唔係同路人<br />\n<br />\n荃灣黑夜 要前線放藍衫走<br />\n結果同一班藍衫轉頭斬斷其他手足手筋腳筋攪到個手足殘廢 同有手足比人爆頭<br />\n到今日岩岩機場 逼手足放個用磚頭爆手足頭既藍絲走<br />\n<br />\n重有依2個月好多單左膠死攬傷人者<br />\n根本班撚樣只係為光環 欺善怕惡<br />\n對住黑社會就淆底唔敢阻黑社會斬人<br />\n對住自己手足 知手足唔會打佢地<br />\n就大大力阻手足還拖 同講廢話訓前線話<br />\n話會扣幾多分 會失民意<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></span></span>"},{"pid":"0b994d524f8e06e72eaff2166c807d4d17860291","tid":1550643,"uid":73143,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:07:16.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span>"},{"pid":"c808e63a9548e9595fc4923b69b87996e42fc808","tid":1550643,"uid":73143,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-07T17:09:04.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">打</span></strong></span><span styl